---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — Celestial Tarot">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Celestial Tarot</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="container content">
    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>Celestial Tarot was born from a deep passion for astrology, tarot, and the cosmic forces that shape our lives. We believe that the stars hold wisdom for everyone — and our mission is to make that wisdom accessible, engaging, and beautifully presented.</p>

    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <p>Through our YouTube channel, social media presence, and this website, we offer:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Zodiac Readings</strong> — In-depth video readings for each sign</li>
      <li><strong>Tarot Insights</strong> — Card interpretations and guidance</li>
      <li><strong>Cosmic Guidance</strong> — Seasonal forecasts and lunar wisdom</li>
      <li><strong>Community</strong> — A space for fellow stargazers to connect</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>To illuminate your path through the cosmos with clarity, compassion, and a touch of celestial magic. Whether you're a seasoned astrology enthusiast or just beginning your cosmic journey, Celestial Tarot is here to guide you.</p>

    <h2>Connect</h2>
    <p>Follow us on <a href="https://youtube.com/@Celestia1Tarot">YouTube</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com/Celestia1Tarot">Twitter</a>, and <a href="https://tiktok.com/@Celestia1Tarot">TikTok</a> for daily cosmic insights.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header { text-align: center; padding: 6rem 0 3rem; }
  .content { max-width: 700px; padding-bottom: 2rem; }
  .content h2 { margin: 2rem 0 1rem; font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .content p { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .content ul { color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0 0 1rem 1.5rem; }
  .content li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
</style>
